<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password - MOUAU ClassMate</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #374151; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      padding: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #f0fdf4 50%, #f8fafc 100%);
    }
    
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #15803d 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1D9D21, #FFF600, #1D9D21);
    }
    
    .logo { 
      font-size: 28px; 
      font-weight: bold; 
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    
    .logo-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
    }
    
    .alert-section {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid #1D9D21;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .alert-section::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 100%;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    }
    
    .button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: white; 
      padding: 14px 35px; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 8px; 
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(29, 157, 33, 0.25);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .button::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
      transition: left 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .button:hover::before {
      left: 0;
    }
    
    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(29, 157, 33, 0.35);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #1D9D21 100%);
    }
    
    .link-box {
      background: #f8fafc; 
      padding: 15px; 
      border-radius: 8px; 
      font-size: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin: 20px 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .link-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      margin-top: 40px; 
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 13px; 
      color: #6b7280;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .footer::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    
    .security-note {
      background: #fffef0;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #FFF600;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .user-name {
      color: #1D9D21;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .action-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #15803d 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .action-badge::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
    }
    
    .action-badge::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
    }
    
    .steps {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .steps::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
    }
    
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      background: #1D9D21;
      color: white;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 12px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .step-number::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: #FFF600;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    
    .highlight {
      color: #1D9D21;
      font-weight: 600;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .highlight::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #FFF600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">MOUAU ClassMate</div>
      <div class="logo-subtitle">Your Academic Partner</div>
      <h1 style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Reset Your Password</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="alert-section">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">Hello <span class="user-name">{{name}}</span>,</p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">We received a request to reset your <span class="highlight">MOUAU ClassMate</span> account password.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="action-badge">
        ðŸ”’ Password Reset Request
      </div>
      
      <p>To reset your password and regain access to your academic resources, please click the button below. This will take you to a secure page where you can create a new password for your account.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">
          Reset Password
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-note">
        <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This password reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> for your protection.
      </div>
      
      <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      
      <div class="link-box">
        {{resetLink}}
      </div>
      
      <div class="steps">
        <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #374151; font-size: 16px;">Quick Steps:</h3>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div>Click the reset link above (expires in 1 hour)</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div>Create a strong new password for your account</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div>Sign in to your account with your new password</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-note">
        <strong>Important:</strong> If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. 
        Your account remains secure, but we recommend reviewing your account security settings.
      </div>
          
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        For your security, we recommend choosing a <span class="highlight">strong, unique password</span> that you haven't used on other platforms.
      </p>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
          <strong>MOUAU ClassMate Team</strong><br>
          Student Management System
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
          This is an automated security message. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
          For assistance, contact our support team through the ClassMate portal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>